WorkItem.Description:
After reading BIFF8 files (Excel 97 - Excel 2003) using Excel5 reader one finds boolean values when one inspects
 
$ws->getStyle('A1')->getProtection()->getLocked()
 
but one should really get values from the set:
 
PHPExcel_Style_Protection::PROTECTION_INHERIT
PHPExcel_Style_Protection::PROTECTION_PROTECTED
PHPExcel_Style_Protection::PROTECTION_UNPROTECTED
WorkItem.Summary: Incorrect cell protection values found when using Excel5 reader
